{"tid":750719,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"W Hotel塌200磅玻璃門 壓斷工人腳","createTime":"2018-07-21T07:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T07:04:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b4b2a321a2790a29d49fe65d421172e1e94118b","tid":750719,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T07:04:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180721/20456310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180721%2F20456310&d=Qe%2BgxeiDsR1%2BVFMYyOZSCFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=1dc482b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180721%2F20456310&h=38c9cd06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180721/20456310</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月21日 <br />\n<br />\nW Hotel塌200磅玻璃門<br />\n壓斷工人腳<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】油麻地九龍站W Hotel發生工傷意外，昨日凌晨零時許，約3至4名工人在地下大堂更換玻璃門，工人換上一扇玻璃門時，該扇約4米乘0.5米、重逾200磅玻璃門疑失平衡塌下，一名姓張49歲工人走避不及，右小腿被壓中骨折受傷。工友協助救出及報警送院。警方對事件展開調查。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n人工心助等換心者爭取時間<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【動畫】P牌寶馬Mini互撼2司機傷"}]}